      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,6 @@\n+created: 2025-12-22\n+title: Improved Context Gathering\n+intro: >-\n+  This release improves the changelog entry creation workflow by providing clearer\n+  guidance for determining which commits to include when adding entries outside of a\n+  pull request context."
